    "querySweep": "for each diet: for each cuisine: for each mealType -> 1 paginated query; cells where estPerQuery=0 are skipped (diet incompatible with that mealType, e.g. keto desserts are sparse)",
    "expectedYield": "sum over diets of (sum of cell estPerQuery) far exceeds each floor; cross-diet dedup-by-URI collapses overlaps so the UNIQUE union lands >= totalFloor with audit headroom",
    "legal": "Edamam = link-out only (instructions=null, instructionsExternal=true, 'Powered by Edamam'). Full method displayed ONLY for themealdb + curated. No scraping anywhere.",
    "qaNote": "topPriorityDishes (the top-1000 pass) are harvested and label-verified BEFORE the matrix sweep so the home rails and 'Most popular' sort are dense and trustworthy from launch."
  },

